com.mydogspies.xflymetar.apis

Class PojoMetar

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mydogspies.xflymetar.apis.PojoMetar

  • public class PojoMetar
extends java.lang.Object
    The Retrofit Pojo for the METAR data from aviationweather.gov. The string dataType denotes which API we got data from. In this case it should be "metar". The boolean apiError is set to TRUE if we fail to get a response as a flag since the object is always passed on no matter what. If API response was successful then it should be FALSE.
    Since:
    0.1.0
